			<div><strong>Mafoos Player Window Version 2.0 Released</strong><br />&nbsp;</div>
		
		
		
		<div>Version 2.0 is a fair change to the basic setup.<br />
I have now incorperated rainbow bars (have to be seen to belived)<br />
%'s have also gone but i will reintroduce them if they are wanted.<br />
LFG/LFM button is in now.<br />
all warning/error messages have been cleaned up so should not cause undue UIErrors.txt and the non-compatable warning!<br />
window size is now 108 by 178. (went on a minamalizing frenzy again)<br />
<br />
Please leave your comments and feedback, i apreciate to know which direction to take things!<br />
(This Thread covers any Version 2.0 mod i have made)<br />
<a href="http://www.eqinterface.com/sdownload/fileinfo.php?s=&amp;id=3258" target="_blank">Group Window</a></div>
	</td>
</tr>
</table>
