			<div><strong>BIG SMILE HERE !</strong><br />&nbsp;</div>
		
		
		
		<div>It is so great to see you are back and playing with your mods.  Norrath without Mafoo was a much sadder place.  I cannot play EQ without your Spell Bar and Player window.  I have always appreciated the look and feel of both of them.<br />
<br />
And while I simply adore your group mod, I have but one true wish.....not that you minimize it any further as all your mods are intrinsically minimized already by design and the content to take up as little screen acreage yet give the maximum amount of information AT A GLANCE, but instead that your group window be sized the same as your player window.  That way, I can place them side by side in the middle of the display on the bottome edge with chat windows on either side.  For those that stack them, they can be placed one atop the other in a seamless column.  <br />
<br />
I know you have been minimizing the group mod, but at the risk of repeating myself, your design is already minimized because of the layout of the information.  You are trying to make something perfect better.  And that is always hard to do.  But in truth, I like the look of the Rainbow alot.  I mean a whole lot!  Great design.<br />
:p <br />
<br />
Thanks for your inspiration and hard work.</div>
	</td>
