			<div><strong>Names Dissapearing</strong><br />&nbsp;</div>
		
		
		
		<div>been playing around with this a bit - got a horizontal version, with function key numbers and percentages - now trying to resolve the dissapearing names issue... I read a post here somewhere that explains why the names dissapear when a group member is out of zone - its because the window uses a seperate &quot;label&quot; for the name rather than the &quot;built in&quot; text that comes with the gauge...<br />
<br />
so,<br />
<br />
my problem is this - there are so many layered gauges that I'm unsure of which one to use for the text - or if it even matters - I seem to recall reading somewhere that it needs to be the gauge thats on the &quot;top&quot; layer for the text to show, but I'm really not sure - if anyone can shed some light I can get this finished pretty quickly - otherwise I'll keep messing with it till I figure it out.</div>
